# Purchasely-Cordova-Sources

## Add plugin :

`cd example/`

`cordova plugin add ../ --link`


## Add android platform :

`cd example/`

`cordova platform add android@latest`

`cordova run android`

## Add iOS platform :

`cd example/`

`cordova platform add ios@latest`

`cordova run ios`

### Add Google-Play dependencies

In folder `example/platforms/android/app` create a file called `build-extras.gradle` and add thoses lines :
```groovy
dependencies {
    implementation "io.purchasely:google-play:3.2.2"
}
```

### Troubleshot

`cd example/`

`cordova platform remove android`

`cordova plugin remove @purchasely/cordova-plugin-purchasely`
